message.body: We received your request and want to thank you for your interest in the Doral 1996 Bounceback Offer. Unfortunately, this offer has expired; therefore your request is being returned. We hope you will continue to patronize our client. Please watch for new offers which may become available. If you have any questions regarding this offer, please call 1-800-926-8814 Monday through Friday.
